Name:		smokeping
Version:	2.0.5
Release:	2.5
License:	GPL v2
Group:		Networking/Utilities
Source0:	http://people.ee.ethz.ch/~oetiker/webtools/smokeping/pub/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	c965439c147012b91585c3e134225b4d
